    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its ownership. Mechanically, it is very solid, with a smooth engine and transmission that make it a pleasure to drive. While the exterior and interior show some minor signs of normal wear, such as light scratches and small upholstery blemishes, the car remains clean and presentable. It is a reliable choice for anyone looking for a dependable vehicle that is ready for the road without needing immediate repairs.",
