    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant mechanical and cosmetic attention from its next owner. The exterior shows noticeable rust on the lower panels and several large dents, while the interior has heavy staining and a significant tear in the driver's seat upholstery. Mechanically, the engine has a persistent oil leak and the transmission hesitates noticeably when shifting, so it is best suited for someone looking for a dedicated project car or a source of parts. It currently runs but is not recommended for long-distance travel without immediate repairs.",
      "price": 4500.0,
